description	"Din Djarin

Class Summary: 
A tanky hybrid melee/gunner with a sniper and flamethrower.

Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2) (Increased damage)
- Amban Phase-Pulse Blaster *
- The Darksaber *
- Wrist Flamethrower

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
---Amban Phase-Pulse Blaster
- Based on Projectile Rifle
- Significantly increased damage
- Reduced reload time

---The Darksaber
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow and Desann styles
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers 

Attributes:
- Fuel (3)
- Regenerating Fuel
- Cortosis
- Magnetic Plating
- Blast Armor
- Melee damage resistance
- Shield Recharge (1)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3)

With his Mandalorian armor and distinctive beskar helmet, Djarin was both well-equipped and enigmatic, a stranger whose past was shrouded in mystery to others."